            Our Core Areas
          Heading link



 
Copy link












                            Research
                    

                Supporting and conducting research on vital public issues.
            












                            Democratic Education
                    

                Our programming is focused on building civic engagement capacity, education, and leadership.
            












                            Engagement
                    

                Providing tools for dynamic, engaged communities.
            












                            Urban Public Policy Fellowship
                    

                Learn more about our undergraduate fellowship.
            











            Recent Research Reports and Publications
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            Knight Foundation National Report
                    

                The Institute produced a report for the Knight Foundation analyzing the results of a nationwide On The Table initiative.
            









                            On the Table Initiative
                    

                IPCE has reported on the findings of the Chicago Community Trust's yearly On The Table initiative.
            









                            Consent Decree Public Engagement Reports
                    

                IPCE has produced multiple public engagement reports on the Police Consent Decree.
            












